  <brief_title>Closed-loop Sedation of Propofol for Patients Undergoing Spinal Anesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Closed-loop Control System of Propofol Versus Manual Control Using Bispectral Index for Controlled Sedation - a Pilot Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
