  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the administration of a standard anesthetic drug
      (propofol) using an automatic, expert-based system versus a manually controlled system by the
      anesthesiologist. In addition, the performance of the decision support system will be
      evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
